
Vitis install Troubleshoot
https://www.daiphys.com/portal/fpga/xilinx/tools/vitis.html

Set locale to "en_US.UTF-8"

	sudo apt-get install language-pack-en
	sudo locale-gen en_US.UTF-8
	sudo update-locale LANG=en_US.UTF-8 LC_MESSAGES=POSIX

	locale
	locale -a

Additional Lis.:

	sudo apt install libtinfo5

After Install run as admin privilige,

	/opt/Xilinx/Vitis/2024.2/scripts/installLibs.sh

